rg/web/20061108091336/http://www.inflames.com/releases/albums/subterranean/default.asp ''Subterranean'' album details]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20061019224811/http://www.inflames.com/releases/albums/subterranean/info.html ''Subterranean'' information]\n\n{{In Flames}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Subterranean (Ep)}}\n[[Category:In Flames albums]]\n[[Category:1995 EPs]]\n", "name_user": "Urgal", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eTrack listing", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Subterranean_(EP)"}
